00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.520
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:18.320
At the very outset, I have to say that truth is what it is.

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:28.800
You cannot change it, you cannot transform it,

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:34.200
and it cannot compromise with you.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:46.600
It is, it has been, it will be the same.

00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:55.720
Whatever I have to tell you tonight

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:59.800
you need not accept it blindfolded.

00:01:07.120 --> 00:01:11.800
We have had already very big problems with these blind faiths.

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:24.800
You should have an open mind like a scientist

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:30.600
and treat this talk as a hypothesis.

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:43.720
But if it is proved then you have to accept as honest people.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:52.720
Because it is for your benevolence,

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:56.000
it is for the benevolence of your country,

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:59.800
it is for the benevolence of the whole world.

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:13.400
The truth is that you are not this body, this mind,

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:19.400
these emotions, intelligence, ego or your conditionings,

00:02:19.600 --> 00:02:23.600
but you are the pure Spirit.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:44.400
We see beautiful flowers around us, it's actually a miracle.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.320
But we take it for granted.

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:58.000
If we ask a doctor, "Who runs our heart?"

00:02:58.240 --> 00:03:01.040
he will say, "The autonomous nervous system."

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:08.840
But who is this 'auto'?

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:13.120
This they cannot answer.

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:18.840
And who does all this living work?

00:03:22.040 --> 00:03:24.040
Who brought forth our evolution?

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:28.520
There is no answer.

00:03:30.520 --> 00:03:32.040
The second truth is

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:37.440
that there is a All-Pervading Power of Divine Love.

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:47.920
It is a subtle energy which does all this living work.

00:03:55.520 --> 00:03:59.440
Now, unless and until

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:05.640
we evolve more than what we are today,

00:04:06.640 --> 00:04:10.520
it's not possible with this human awareness

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:16.320
to feel the existence of this All-Pervading Power.

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:32.520
And if you have to have this ascent,

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:38.640
then you have to just have pure desire for it.

00:04:46.640 --> 00:04:48.920
The pure desire

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:53.920
is a desire from our mundane desire is very different.

00:05:00.520 --> 00:05:05.640
According to economics, wants are not satiable in general.

00:05:10.440 --> 00:05:14.440
Today we want to have a house, then a car,

00:05:14.640 --> 00:05:20.240
then a helicopter, goes on like that.

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:31.240
But the pure desire of which you are not aware is this

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.960
that you want to evolve

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:38.760
and to feel this union with this All-Pervading Power.

00:05:48.440 --> 00:05:51.840
To feel this All-Pervading Power,

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:58.760
to be in union with it is the yoga, spiritual yoga.

