So the first thing we have to know that,

00:18:59.040 --> 00:19:01.960
you cannot pay for your spirituality.

00:19:07.560 --> 00:19:11.440
I know there have been many who tried to exploit

00:19:11.640 --> 00:19:15.840
all over the world, but they are mostly now exposed.

00:19:25.640 --> 00:19:27.960
I would say it was your mistake

00:19:28.160 --> 00:19:30.840
because how much did you pay to Christ?

00:19:39.240 --> 00:19:46.440
Now, one has to understand that I'm talking about Divine love.

00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:55.240
They all talk of love, all right,

00:19:57.440 --> 00:20:00.840
but it's the actualization of that Divine love.

00:20:04.960 --> 00:20:07.360
It is the becoming which is important,

00:20:09.840 --> 00:20:11.760
not just talking about it.

00:20:14.560 --> 00:20:18.240
There has been lot of talk, we are this, we are that.

00:20:24.640 --> 00:20:28.240
So you become extremely dynamic with this power,

00:20:28.480 --> 00:20:32.240
at the same time extremely compassionate.

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:41.280
You don't have to suggest, you don't have to think,

00:20:41.480 --> 00:20:43.880
you just - you become compassionate.

00:20:50.560 --> 00:20:52.880
The compassion just works.

00:20:55.360 --> 00:21:02.560
Then another thing is that we think about future and past.

00:21:09.080 --> 00:21:12.960
The thought rises, falls, another thought rises and falls,

00:21:13.160 --> 00:21:18.360
and we are jumping on the cusp of future and past.

00:21:26.880 --> 00:21:28.960
We cannot be in the present,

00:21:33.680 --> 00:21:35.560
which is the reality.

00:21:37.480 --> 00:21:39.160
Present is the reality.

00:21:41.160 --> 00:21:46.360
The past is finished, and the future doesn't exist.

00:21:51.160 --> 00:21:53.680
When the Kundalini rises

00:21:53.960 --> 00:21:58.360
She elongates those thoughts and establishes in the center

00:21:59.560 --> 00:22:04.360
where there is complete thoughtless awareness.

00:22:15.280 --> 00:22:19.480
And spiritually you grow in that thoughtless awareness

00:22:19.680 --> 00:22:23.680
which in Sanskrit we call as Nirvichaar Samadhi.

00:22:34.680 --> 00:22:38.880
The second state we call as Nirvikalpa Samadhi means

00:22:39.080 --> 00:22:40.560
doubtless awareness,

00:22:47.280 --> 00:22:49.560
when you become your own master.

00:22:52.960 --> 00:22:57.360
Because in the light of the Spirit you know what is the truth is.

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:05.080
What is destructive for you and what is constructive for you.

00:23:09.080 --> 00:23:14.080
And you just disregard all that is destructive.

00:23:18.200 --> 00:23:21.600
I don't have to tell you, "Don't do this, don't - no."

00:23:25.080 --> 00:23:27.600
If I say that, half of you will go away.

00:23:31.880 --> 00:23:36.480
It's like this, supposing I have a snake in My hand,

00:23:40.880 --> 00:23:42.080
and I am very adamant

00:23:44.400 --> 00:23:46.280
and it's darkness

00:23:48.280 --> 00:23:51.800
and somebody says that,  "There's a snake in your hand."

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:53.960
I will say, "No, it is a rope."

00:23:59.680 --> 00:24:03.200
Until the snake bites Me I will say, "It's a rope."

00:24:07.800 --> 00:24:09.880
But if there is little light

00:24:10.800 --> 00:24:12.880
immediately I will throw away the snake.

00:24:16.800 --> 00:24:18.200
Nobody has to tell you.

00:24:19.680 --> 00:24:24.400
This is how your attention becomes enlightened,

00:24:24.680 --> 00:24:28.880
and you become a very wise and sane personality.

00:24:35.400 --> 00:24:37.800
And then you understand your value,

00:24:39.880 --> 00:24:41.480
your identity.

00:24:42.480 --> 00:24:46.960
Then you know you have become the instrument of this Divine love.

00:24:50.960 --> 00:24:52.600
It's a pure love.

00:24:56.400 --> 00:24:58.960
Like a sap rises in a tree,

00:24:59.320 --> 00:25:03.880
it gives whatever is needed for every part of the tree

00:25:04.200 --> 00:25:06.600
- ultimately it evaporates.

00:25:15.720 --> 00:25:17.800
But supposing it likes one flower,

00:25:21.120 --> 00:25:22.720
gets attached.

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:28.200
Then the tree will die and the flower will die also.

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:34.320
So this detachment comes from within.

00:25:38.200 --> 00:25:44.520
It's not to wear these dresses of renouncing

00:25:44.800 --> 00:25:48.400
or to shave your head, that's not needed.

00:25:54.400 --> 00:25:56.120
It's an inner happening.

00:25:57.600 --> 00:25:59.800
You don't have to give up your families,

00:26:00.120 --> 00:26:02.200
you don't have to give up your jobs,

00:26:02.400 --> 00:26:04.600
you have to be absolutely normal.

00:26:10.720 --> 00:26:13.520
But when you become thoughtlessly aware,

00:26:13.800 --> 00:26:16.000
the peace is established within.

00:26:21.720 --> 00:26:25.200
I have known many people who have got peace awards,

00:26:25.520 --> 00:26:28.520
this award, that award - they have no peace within,

00:26:28.800 --> 00:26:30.200
I don't know how they got it.

00:26:39.600 --> 00:26:42.120
Actually most of them are very hot tempered.

00:26:42.320 --> 00:26:45.920
If you have to reach them you have to take a barge pole, somehow.

00:26:57.400 --> 00:26:59.600
You establish your peace within

00:27:02.920 --> 00:27:07.520
and then the whole world becomes like a drama.

00:27:10.920 --> 00:27:14.240
You get out of your problems and see them clearly.

00:27:19.320 --> 00:27:23.920
Like if you are standing in the water you are afraid of the waves,

00:27:28.240 --> 00:27:31.520
but if you get into the boat you can see the waves.

00:27:35.520 --> 00:27:39.640
But if you know how to swim you can jump in and save many others.

00:27:43.920 --> 00:27:45.920
This is how Sahaja Yoga works.

00:27:51.720 --> 00:27:56.640
