When we see television, we know about the ether.

00:28:22.840 --> 00:28:25.920
But I am talking about the subtle of the ether,

00:28:28.640 --> 00:28:34.240
which is so efficient, which is so fast,

00:28:34.520 --> 00:28:39.840
which is so active, and which is so loving.

00:28:47.640 --> 00:28:50.520
