00:35:19.600 --> 00:35:25.200
self-confident that you are going to get your Self-Realization.

00:35:38.280 --> 00:35:42.680
That means you should not condemn yourself for anything.

00:35:46.960 --> 00:35:48.960
You should not feel guilty.

00:35:50.280 --> 00:35:53.600
Guilty at all about anything that has happened in the past.

00:35:58.200 --> 00:36:00.280
At this moment the past is finished.

00:36:03.080 --> 00:36:05.600
Unfortunately if you feel guilty,

00:36:05.880 --> 00:36:08.800
then this center catches very badly

00:36:14.680 --> 00:36:17.800
and you get disease called angina,

00:36:18.080 --> 00:36:23.080
also spondylitis, and also lethargic organs.

00:36:30.400 --> 00:36:32.680
It's a fashion to feel guilty.

00:36:34.800 --> 00:36:37.680
I mean, some people feel guilty for their forefathers,

00:36:37.960 --> 00:36:40.880
some feel guilty, say for Rwanda people,

00:36:41.200 --> 00:36:42.880
you can't help these things.

00:36:50.400 --> 00:36:51.200
It's a myth.

00:36:55.200 --> 00:37:01.480
And at this moment it's important that please don't feel guilty,

00:37:06.600 --> 00:37:09.960
because the Kundalini will stop at this center.

00:37:13.400 --> 00:37:16.400
All your life you have tortured yourself and now

00:37:16.720 --> 00:37:21.520
at this important moment you should not feel guilty,

00:37:21.800 --> 00:37:23.800
so the Kundalini doesn't rise

00:37:23.800 --> 00:37:26.400
and you miss your Self-Realization.

00:37:43.200 --> 00:37:47.120
In short you should be presently

00:37:47.400 --> 00:37:49.600
pleasantly placed towards yourself.

00:37:53.720 --> 00:37:57.600
As I respect you, you must respect yourself.

00:38:01.600 --> 00:38:04.200
As I love you, you must love yourself.

00:38:07.520 --> 00:38:09.800
That's all I want.

00:38:11.720 --> 00:38:14.520
The second condition is

00:38:14.800 --> 00:38:20.200
that you have to forgive everyone in general,

00:38:25.800 --> 00:38:29.520
that means you don't even have to think about

00:38:29.800 --> 00:38:31.920
whom you have to forgive,

00:38:36.920 --> 00:38:38.720
because that's a headache.

00:38:40.320 --> 00:38:44.120
Logically, whether you forgive or you don't forgive

00:38:44.400 --> 00:38:45.520
you don't do anything.

00:38:51.000 --> 00:38:52.120
It's a myth.

00:38:53.400 --> 00:38:56.520
But if you don't forgive then you play into wrong hands,

00:39:00.600 --> 00:39:04.920
and the center on the optic chiasma is like this - constricted.

00:39:09.400 --> 00:39:12.920
At this moment, if you don't forgive it won't open like this

00:39:17.240 --> 00:39:19.000
and you will miss your chance,

00:39:19.320 --> 00:39:22.720
such an important thing of Self-Realization.

00:39:28.320 --> 00:39:31.920
So please forgive - in general I say.

00:39:35.720 --> 00:39:42.120
Now, the third condition is

00:39:43.240 --> 00:39:45.440
you have to take out your shoes.

00:39:52.320 --> 00:39:54.440
Because this Mother Earth helps us.

00:39:57.720 --> 00:40:00.520
Many people don't like the third condition sometimes.

00:40:03.840 --> 00:40:05.920
In England, first time when I asked them

00:40:06.240 --> 00:40:10.240
to take out their shoes, half of them walked off

00:40:19.120 --> 00:40:20.640
very seriously.

00:40:38.520 --> 00:40:44.120
Now, somebody will show you.

00:40:51.320 --> 00:40:55.720
First you should see what we are going to do.

00:40:59.640 --> 00:41:05.520
He must have told you that we have two channels, left and right

00:41:07.040 --> 00:41:12.320
which are opposite to each other but are complimentary.

00:41:22.040 --> 00:41:28.520
They look after the sympathetic nervous systems, left and right.

00:41:32.840 --> 00:41:37.440
So the left one is for the power of desire, by which we desire,

00:41:37.720 --> 00:41:38.720
mundane desire,

00:41:43.720 --> 00:41:48.240
and in the right we have the power of action.

00:41:50.840 --> 00:41:55.640
So you have to put your both feet apart from each other.

00:42:02.640 --> 00:42:06.040
And put your left hand on your left lap

00:42:06.320 --> 00:42:11.240
like this very comfortably.

00:42:17.760 --> 00:42:21.240
This is suggestive and symbolic

00:42:21.560 --> 00:42:25.560
of your desire to have Self-Realization.

00:42:31.040 --> 00:42:34.560
So we use our right hand for the action.

00:42:38.160 --> 00:42:41.160
Please be seated,

00:42:41.440 --> 00:42:43.560
we have room here for you.

00:42:46.560 --> 00:42:49.240
All of you have to sit down, please,

00:42:51.240 --> 00:42:52.560
be comfortable.

00:42:55.040 --> 00:42:56.960
You don't have to go to Himalaya,

00:42:57.240 --> 00:43:00.440
stand on your head, shave off your hair, nothing of the kind.

00:43:05.360 --> 00:43:06.640
Be comfortable.

00:43:08.640 --> 00:43:13.840
So, now we put our right hand on our heart.

00:43:18.160 --> 00:43:20.840
In the heart resides the Spirit.

00:43:24.440 --> 00:43:26.640
Now if you become the Spirit,

00:43:27.160 --> 00:43:31.240
you become your own guide and your own master.

00:43:37.240 --> 00:43:41.360
Now take down your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen

00:43:41.640 --> 00:43:43.160
on the left hand side.

00:43:48.360 --> 00:43:50.560
We are working only on the left hand side.

00:43:54.360 --> 00:43:58.440
Here is the center for your mastery.

00:44:01.160 --> 00:44:05.760
Mastery over yourself and mastery over the knowledge,

00:44:06.080 --> 00:44:08.480
the pure Divine knowledge.

00:44:13.960 --> 00:44:18.680
It's created by great prophets and seers,

00:44:22.160 --> 00:44:23.680
which is to be enlightened.

00:44:26.160 --> 00:44:29.160
Now take down your hand into the lower portion of your abdomen

00:44:29.360 --> 00:44:30.880
on the left hand side.

00:44:35.680 --> 00:44:40.360
Surprisingly this is the center for pure Divine knowledge.

00:44:45.080 --> 00:44:49.280
Now raise your right hand on the upper portion of your abdomen.

00:44:52.560 --> 00:44:53.880
Then on your heart.

00:44:55.080 --> 00:44:57.280
Then in the corner of your neck and shoulder

00:44:57.560 --> 00:44:59.280
and turn your head to your right.

00:45:04.360 --> 00:45:07.960
Oh. It is there, that means you are feeling guilty.

00:45:08.280 --> 00:45:09.560
Please don't feel guilty.

00:45:18.760 --> 00:45:23.480
Now, take your right hand on top of your forehead across

00:45:23.680 --> 00:45:25.480
and put down your head

00:45:32.280 --> 00:45:36.480
this is the center where you have to ask for forgiveness

00:45:36.760 --> 00:45:38.960
or forgive everyone.

00:45:46.560 --> 00:45:49.160
In general without thinking about them.

00:45:51.680 --> 00:45:54.760
Now take back your right hand on the back side of your head

00:45:54.960 --> 00:45:57.760
and push back your head as far as possible.

00:46:02.560 --> 00:46:05.880
This is the center where without feeling guilty,

00:46:06.160 --> 00:46:09.560
without counting your mistakes for your own satisfaction

00:46:09.880 --> 00:46:12.280
you have to ask  forgiveness

00:46:12.480 --> 00:46:16.280
from the All-Pervading Power of Divine love.

00:46:32.800 --> 00:46:37.200
Now, the last center is very important, stretch your palm fully.

00:46:44.600 --> 00:46:49.400
Now put the center of your palm on top of the fontanel bone area

00:46:49.600 --> 00:46:52.400
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

00:47:01.200 --> 00:47:03.960
Now push back your fingers, it's very important,

00:47:04.280 --> 00:47:06.880
so that there's a good pressure on your scalp.

00:47:13.800 --> 00:47:15.280
Now put down your head

00:47:17.200 --> 00:47:20.280
and move your scalp slowly 16

00:47:23.680 --> 00:47:28.600
- 7 times, 7 times, clockwise.

00:47:44.200 --> 00:47:46.480
Now, that's all we have to do.

00:47:48.200 --> 00:47:51.200
But please remember to push back your fingers.

00:47:56.080 --> 00:48:03.200
Now again, see that your both legs are apart from each other,

00:48:03.480 --> 00:48:06.200
and the left hand is on your left lap.

00:48:16.200 --> 00:48:20.880
You can close your eyes and take out your spectacles,

00:48:21.200 --> 00:48:24.080
please don't open your eyes till I tell you.

00:48:33.800 --> 00:48:36.480
So now, put your right hand on your heart

00:48:39.800 --> 00:48:41.400
and close your eyes.

00:48:44.600 --> 00:48:48.680
Here you have to ask Me a very fundamental

00:48:49.000 --> 00:48:51.480
question about yourself

00:48:51.800 --> 00:48:55.320
- you can call Me Shri Mataji or Mother.

00:48:58.120 --> 00:49:06.320
Please say three times, "Mother, am I the Spirit?"

00:49:07.920 --> 00:49:09.320
Say in your heart.

00:49:35.320 --> 00:49:37.920
As I told you, when you are the Spirit

00:49:38.120 --> 00:49:41.600
you become your own guide, your own master.

00:49:49.720 --> 00:49:52.120
So now please bring your right hand

00:49:52.320 --> 00:49:55.000
in the upper portion of your abdomen on the left hand side

00:49:55.200 --> 00:50:00.320
and here you ask another fundamental question about yourself,

00:50:00.520 --> 00:50:06.800
three times in your heart, "Mother, am I my own master?"

00:50:30.520 --> 00:50:33.800
I have already told you that I respect your freedom

00:50:34.120 --> 00:50:37.120
and I cannot force Self-Realization

00:50:37.400 --> 00:50:42.600
or pure Divine knowledge on you

00:50:42.920 --> 00:50:46.320
- so you have to ask for it.

00:50:57.800 --> 00:50:59.600
So now, please take your right hand

00:50:59.920 --> 00:51:01.720
in the lower portion of your abdomen

00:51:02.200 --> 00:51:08.800
and ask six times, because this center has got six petals,

00:51:09.120 --> 00:51:14.320
"Mother, please give me pure Divine knowledge."

00:51:32.720 --> 00:51:38.320
As soon as you ask for the pure divine knowledge

00:51:38.520 --> 00:51:42.120
the Kundalini starts rising within you.

00:51:42.400 --> 00:51:47.320
So we have to nourish our upper centers

00:51:47.520 --> 00:51:51.120
with our full self-confidence.

00:52:08.120 --> 00:52:12.320
So now raise your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen

00:52:12.640 --> 00:52:13.840
on the left hand side.

00:52:19.320 --> 00:52:23.920
Here you have to say with full confidence ten times,

00:52:24.240 --> 00:52:27.920
"Mother, I am my own master."

00:52:38.320 --> 00:52:40.920
At the very outset, I told you

00:52:41.240 --> 00:52:45.440
that you are not this body, this mind,

00:52:45.640 --> 00:52:49.320
these emotions, this intelligence, these conditionings,

00:52:49.640 --> 00:52:53.240
and the ego, but you are the pure Spirit.

00:53:06.520 --> 00:53:09.240
So raise your right hand on your heart

00:53:10.520 --> 00:53:15.040
and say with full confidence again, twelve times,

00:53:15.320 --> 00:53:18.640
"Mother, I am the pure Spirit."

00:53:33.120 --> 00:53:36.920
This All-Pervading Divine Power of Love

00:53:37.240 --> 00:53:40.640
is the ocean of knowledge,

00:53:40.920 --> 00:53:46.640
is the ocean of bliss and compassion,

00:53:58.720 --> 00:54:02.920
but above all it is the ocean of forgiveness.

00:54:06.840 --> 00:54:09.120
So whatever mistakes you might have committed

00:54:09.320 --> 00:54:13.920
can be easily dissolved by this ocean of forgiveness at this moment.

00:54:20.640 --> 00:54:22.840
So please forgive yourself

00:54:25.320 --> 00:54:29.240
and raise your right hand in the corner of your neck and shoulder

00:54:29.440 --> 00:54:31.440
and turn your head to your right.

00:54:37.760 --> 00:54:40.440
Here you have to say 16 times,

00:54:41.360 --> 00:54:46.560
"Mother I am not guilty at all."

00:54:47.360 --> 00:54:49.360
Say it with full confidence.

00:54:58.840 --> 00:55:04.760
I have already told you that logically,

00:55:04.960 --> 00:55:08.560
whether you forgive or don't forgive you don't do anything.

00:55:14.240 --> 00:55:15.440
It is a myth,

00:55:16.760 --> 00:55:22.560
but you are playing into wrong hands and torturing yourself.

00:55:24.840 --> 00:55:28.960
At this moment, if you do not forgive,

00:55:29.640 --> 00:55:35.240
the center of Agnya won't open and the Kundalini won't rise.

00:55:35.960 --> 00:55:41.960
So please, please forgive, forgive everyone in general.

00:55:58.960 --> 00:56:02.360
By raising your hand on top of your forehead,

00:56:02.640 --> 00:56:03.640
put down your head.

00:56:09.960 --> 00:56:11.240
And here you say,

00:56:11.840 --> 00:56:17.440
"Mother, I forgive everyone in general."

00:56:39.960 --> 00:56:41.640
Now without feeling guilty,

00:56:41.960 --> 00:56:45.360
without counting your mistakes for your satisfaction

00:56:45.640 --> 00:56:51.240
you have to ask forgiveness from the All-Pervading Divine Power.

00:57:01.240 --> 00:57:04.160
So please take your right hand on the back side of your head

00:57:04.480 --> 00:57:06.240
and push back your head.

00:57:13.080 --> 00:57:16.280
Here you have to say,

00:57:16.560 --> 00:57:21.160
"Oh Divine power, please forgive me,

00:57:21.360 --> 00:57:26.360
if I have done any mistakes, knowingly or unknowingly."

00:57:26.680 --> 00:57:28.880
Please say it in your heart, not how many times.

00:57:49.280 --> 00:57:55.960
Now the last center you have to stretch your palm fully,

00:57:56.280 --> 00:58:01.360
put the center of your palm on top of your fontanel bone area

00:58:02.080 --> 00:58:05.280
and put down your head.

00:58:15.880 --> 00:58:17.160
Here again,

00:58:17.680 --> 00:58:22.280
I cannot force Self-Realization on you, you have to ask for it.

00:58:27.280 --> 00:58:29.760
Now, push back your fingers,

00:58:31.080 --> 00:58:34.480
put a pressure on your scalp

00:58:34.760 --> 00:58:38.560
and move it seven times saying,

00:58:40.760 --> 00:58:46.480
"Mother, please give me my Self-Realization",

00:58:46.480 --> 00:58:50.960
clockwise you have to move.

00:59:34.560 --> 00:59:36.160
Push back your fingers

00:59:38.560 --> 00:59:41.160
and move the scalp clockwise.

00:59:46.560 --> 00:59:48.880
Please bend your heads, bend your heads.

00:59:54.160 --> 01:00:00.760
Now, take down your hands

01:00:01.080 --> 01:00:04.360
and please open your eyes slowly.

01:00:08.680 --> 01:00:11.280
Put both the hands towards Me

01:00:11.480 --> 01:00:14.400
and watch Me without thinking.

01:00:22.880 --> 01:00:25.800
Now put the right hand towards Me

01:00:26.080 --> 01:00:30.800
and put the left hand on top of the fontanel bone area

01:00:31.080 --> 01:00:35.400
and see for yourself if there's a cool, or a hot,

01:00:35.680 --> 01:00:38.080
breeze-like vibrations are coming

01:00:38.280 --> 01:00:40.960
out of your own fontanel bone area.

01:00:42.280 --> 01:00:44.200
Now please put your left hand towards Me.

01:00:46.960 --> 01:00:49.480
And now see with the right hand

01:00:49.800 --> 01:00:53.800
if there is a cool or a hot breeze-like vibrations

01:00:54.080 --> 01:00:57.960
coming from your own fontanel bone area.

01:01:09.280 --> 01:01:11.480
If it is hot means you have not forgiven.

01:01:11.680 --> 01:01:13.800
Please forgive now, at this moment.

01:01:22.080 --> 01:01:24.680
Now, again with the right hand once again.

01:01:28.960 --> 01:01:30.080
Please bend your head.

01:01:41.400 --> 01:01:45.600
Now raise both your hands towards the sky,

01:01:45.880 --> 01:01:47.400
push back your head.

01:01:52.880 --> 01:01:57.080
Here you have to ask one of these three questions three times.

01:02:03.400 --> 01:02:05.200
First one is,

01:02:05.480 --> 01:02:09.480
"Mother, is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?"

01:02:15.480 --> 01:02:18.320
Second is, "Mother

01:02:19.120 --> 01:02:23.120
is this the All-Pervading Power of Divine Love,

01:02:28.600 --> 01:02:30.120
is this the Ruh?"

01:02:31.800 --> 01:02:36.400
The third is, "Mother, is this the Paramachaitanya?"

01:02:40.120 --> 01:02:42.720
Ask anyone of these questions three times.

01:02:49.000 --> 01:02:51.720
Now, take down your hands.

01:02:54.000 --> 01:02:56.400
Please put your hands to Me.

01:03:02.400 --> 01:03:09.800
All those who have felt the cool breeze on the fingertips

01:03:10.920 --> 01:03:17.320
or on the palm or through their fontanel bone area,

01:03:17.600 --> 01:03:21.520
cool breeze or hot breeze, raise both your hands.

01:03:42.320 --> 01:03:43.600
May God bless you all,

01:03:43.800 --> 01:03:47.920
you all have become saints now, I bow to you.

01:03:54.400 --> 01:03:58.920
Now respect your Self-Realization.

01:04:01.920 --> 01:04:03.600
Still you have to grow.

01:04:06.000 --> 01:04:11.800
We have to understand that this is a collective process.

01:04:15.200 --> 01:04:18.000
You cannot do it alone anyway.

01:04:19.520 --> 01:04:22.000
So you have to come to collective.

01:04:24.720 --> 01:04:27.400
Of course, you don't have to pay at all for anything.

01:04:30.720 --> 01:04:32.320
But you have to give some time,

01:04:32.600 --> 01:04:35.800
some importance to your Self-Realization.

01:04:41.720 --> 01:04:46.920
So please, make it a point to come to the collective.

01:04:52.440 --> 01:04:54.720
Very surprising, you don't know Me,

01:04:54.920 --> 01:04:56.840
I am not an Austrian,

01:04:56.920 --> 01:05:00.440
but when I come always the halls are full,

01:05:00.720 --> 01:05:05.920
but when I go away they don't follow up, I don't know why.

01:05:16.320 --> 01:05:20.120
Only in Russia, I have seen people have gone very deep,

01:05:20.320 --> 01:05:24.920
they are so deep people, very deep people.

01:05:30.840 --> 01:05:34.320
Once they get Realization they just get to it.

01:05:38.920 --> 01:05:41.040
It's very surprising.

01:05:42.520 --> 01:05:45.440
So I have to make a request to you

01:05:45.720 --> 01:05:48.720
that though you have got it everything

01:05:49.040 --> 01:05:52.640
so easily you have to grow into it.

01:06:00.040 --> 01:06:02.320
You have to have the whole knowledge.

01:06:05.040 --> 01:06:10.040
I must have spoken only in English language at least

01:06:10.240 --> 01:06:13.640
- there must be 4'000, 5'000 lectures.

01:06:19.320 --> 01:06:25.320
But they are only indications to know

01:06:25.640 --> 01:06:29.840
what you are and to experience it.

01:06:34.440 --> 01:06:37.320
Sahaja Yoga is an experience.

01:06:39.640 --> 01:06:44.240
In Sanskrit, we have a word called Budha or Vida

01:06:49.640 --> 01:06:54.440
that means to know the knowledge on your central nervous system.

01:07:00.240 --> 01:07:02.840
From Budha the word Buddha has come.

01:07:03.160 --> 01:07:06.840
From Vida the word Vedas has come.

01:07:14.840 --> 01:07:18.360
So this knowledge is your own.

01:07:18.640 --> 01:07:22.040
It was the ancient treasure,

01:07:22.360 --> 01:07:25.440
but now is available to all of us.

01:07:32.360 --> 01:07:37.560
So please try to understand the importance of your being.

01:07:41.360 --> 01:07:43.560
I always come after one year

01:07:43.840 --> 01:07:46.560
and I hope to come back to see you all.

01:07:53.160 --> 01:07:54.360
May God bless you!

01:08:33.360 --> 01:08:37.440
Thank you very much! May God bless you all!
